│ ### Step 2: Propose a Fix                                    │
│                                                              │
│ My proposed fix is to modify the condition that triggers the │
│ `copysign(x, y) -> copysign(x, -1.0)` transformation. The    │
│ current condition is:                                        │
│                                                              │
│ ```cpp                                                       │
│ if (HasPositive && !HasNegative && !(FPClass & FC_Pos)) {    │
│ ```                                                          │
│                                                              │
│ This incorrectly assumes that if the result is not in any of │
│ the positive floating-point classes (`FC_Pos`), it must be a │
