│ if (HasPositive && !HasNegative && !(FPClass & (FC_Pos |     │
│ FC_QNaN | FC_SNaN))) {                                       │
│ ```                                                          │
│                                                              │
│ This ensures the optimization is only applied when the       │
│ result is guaranteed to be a negative number, making it safe │
│ in the presence of potential NaN inputs.                     │
